filter_description:
Currently supports filtering by tags and creation time. Fill in the format as follows:
{
  "tags": {
    "$and": ["Tag 1","Tag 2"],
    "$or": ["When there are $and tags, and is effective, or is not effective"]
  },
  "createTime": {
      "$gte": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm format, collection creation time greater than this time",
      "$lte": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm format, collection creation time less than this time, can be used with $gte"
  }
}
